{"div":{"@":{"xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","type":"article","xml:id":"MG-1678-04_181","resp":"mercure"},"#":[{"head":{"value":"[Vers de M. Robbe à Monseigneur le Dauphin]","id":"/div/#[0]/head"}},{"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/#[1]/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", avril 1678 [tome 4], p. 181-182.","id":"/div/#[1]/bibl/#"}}},{"p":{"#1":{"value":"Dans le temps du Départ, M","id":"/div/#[2]/p/#1"},"hi":{"@rend":"sup","#":{"value":"r","id":"/div/#[2]/p/hi/#"}},"#2":{"value":" Robbe fit ce Madrigal pour Monseigneur le Dauphin.","id":"/div/#[2]/p/#2"}}},{"quote":{"l":["Le Printemps vient à peine de renaistre,",{"space":{},"#":{"value":"Et mille desseins glorieux","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/l[1]/#"}},{"space":{},"#":{"value":"Emportent nostre Auguste Maistre","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/l[2]/#"}},"Déja bien loin de ces aimables lieux ;","Et cependant la joye &amp; l’abondance,",{"space":{},"#":{"value":"Les Jeux, les Plaisirs, les Amours,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/l[5]/#"}},{"space":{},"#":{"value":"Par vostre charmante présence,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/l[6]/#"}},{"space":[{},{}],"#":{"value":"Y regnent toûjours.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/l[7]/#"}}]}},{"p":{"#1":{"value":"Cecy est du mesme M","id":"/div/#[4]/p/#1"},"hi":{"@rend":"sup","#":{"value":"r","id":"/div/#[4]/p/hi/#"}},"#2":{"value":" Robbe.","id":"/div/#[4]/p/#2"}}},{"quote":{"@rend":"border","label":[{"@rend":"center","#":{"value":"Pour Monseigneur","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/label[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"center","#":{"value":"le Dauphin.","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/label[1]/#"}}],"lg":[{"l":["Jeune Soleil qui brillez","Sur nos Campagnes fleuries,","Et faites de nos Prairies","Des Parterres émaillez ;","Quelle Nympe si légere","Tiendra contre vos attraits ?","Non, la plus fiere Bergere","Ne s’en défendra jamais."]},{"l":["Vos vœux seront fortunez,","Soyez seur de la Victoire ;","Mais craignez pour vostre gloire","De trouver peu de Daphnez,","Car les respects du Tonnerre","Un jour pour vos faits guerriers","Ne laisseront